column1: IF ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_pd_d is MF 1 AND ccr_zoa_dhf_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 AND ccr_llb_oh_andro_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_etio_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_testosterone_d is MF 2 AND ccr_cortisone_d is MF 2 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 1  5_ExtremeObese is 1
